            <title>Pokémon Center TAIPEI 開幕，屬海外第二間</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/09/pokemon-center-taipei-2/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pokemon-center-taipei-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/09/pokemon-center-taipei-2/hottopic/walk/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 09:04:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩樂好去處]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokemon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokémon Center]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokémon Center TAIPEI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1209303</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Pokémon Center TAIPEI 於今（8 日）在台灣<strong>新光三越</strong> 台北信義新天地 A11 3 樓<strong>開幕</strong> ，期間推出不少台灣特色例如夜市、水果為主題的限量商品。只要在開幕期間消費夠指定金額，即可獲得開幕紀念特典卡。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209307 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-694x461.png" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-694x461.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-1280x849.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-768x510.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-1536x1019.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Pokémon Center TAIPEI</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Pokémon Center TAIPEI 除了是台灣第一間 Pokémon Center 外，亦是非日本本土第二間 Pokémon Center，店面設計是以「天空與海洋環繞的風景」為靈感。店面會有啟暴龍和比卡超塑像歡迎顧客。店內陳列多款 Pokémon 商品，而日後也會舉辦不同 Pokémon 相關活動。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209304 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-694x466.png" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-694x466.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-1280x860.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-768x516.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-1536x1032.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Pokémon Center TAIPEI</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">是次開幕有數量總計達 29 款的開幕紀念商品，有 Pokémon Center TAIPEI Pokémon 悠遊卡，純金打造、以 Pokémon Center TAIPEI 標誌設計，售價新台幣 15 萬元的純金徽標，Pokémon Center TAIPEI 設計款比卡超、啟暴龍等毛絨玩具，還有環保袋、附蓋濾茶杯、橡膠掛繩、浴巾、紙膠帶套組、側開筆記本、徽標胸針、杯套、附蓋環保吸管、貼紙套組、便當袋、茶壺、附拉鏈毛巾、墊子、箱型便利貼、A4 文件夾、餐墊餐具套組等商品。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209306 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-1280x848.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-768x509.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-1536x1017.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有數量總計達 29 款的開幕紀念商品</p><p>▲資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://atctwn.com/2023/12/08/80297/">ATC</a>，<a href="https://news.gamebase.com.tw/news/detail/99417922">遊戲基地</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

====
