            <title>Windows 11 記事本終顯示字符數量，更新後有標籤頁、黑暗模式等功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/09/windows-11-notepad/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=windows-11-notepad</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/09/windows-11-notepad/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 09:04:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[應用軟件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Windows 11]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Windows 11 Notepad]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1209310</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">近年來，微軟一直在逐步改進 Windows 11 上的內置記事本，現在終於有了計數功能。在全新的 Windows 11 Canary 測試版本中，微軟在底部添加了字符數字，就像微軟 Word 一樣。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209385 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-4.46.32-PM-694x465.png" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-4.46.32-PM-694x465.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-4.46.32-PM-1280x857.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-4.46.32-PM-768x514.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-4.46.32-PM-1536x1029.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-4.46.32-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div><p align="center">▲<span lang="ZH-TW">全新的</span> Windows 11 Canary <span lang="ZH-TW">測試版本中，微軟在底部添加了字符數字</span></p><p align="center"></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">微軟的 Windows Insider 團隊指：「選擇文字時，狀態欄會顯示選中文字和整個文檔的字數，如果沒有揀選文字，則會顯示整個文檔的字數，用家確保始終能清楚地看到文檔的長度。」</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">這是今年記事本一系列變化中最新增加的一項，最近該應用新增了一個自動儲存選項，用家可在每次關閉時都不會看到彈出的儲存提示。微軟還為記事本添加了標籤頁、黑暗模式。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/7/23992413/microsoft-windows-11-notepad-character-count-widgets-improvements">The Verge</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

