                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">2023 年的香港車壇壓軸登場：皇冠汽車為香港駕駛者帶來 Toyota 首部純電動車 ALL-NEW bZ4X；新車搭載 Toyota 純電車專屬的 eTNGA 底盤，擁有前衞外型及流線車身，同時提供寬敞的車箱空間。bZ4X 將於本週末（12 月 9 至 10 日）在沙田新城市廣場及各大豐田陳列室登場！</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209493 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Toyota ALL-NEW bZ4X</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>車身設計具科技感</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">「科技感」與「前衞」是 bZ4X 的代名詞。車身外型設計穩健硬朗，有跑格的設計語調，車身線條流暢，低腰線貼近輪圈。 車頭採用了錘頭式設計並配置「4 眼」LED 頭燈及一體式尾燈組合；車頭頂部及兩側，車尾特有的左右獨立尾翼均具空氣力學擾流設計，降低風阻並提供更穩定的行車與續航表現，亦配備 20 吋合金輪圈，配合全黑色及 5 款雙色車身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209495 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209496 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209497 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209498 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209503 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲車頭採用了錘頭式設計並配置「4 眼」LED 頭燈及一體式尾燈組合</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>車裏</strong><strong>空間</strong><strong>感舒服度高</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">bZ4X 的空間感與舒適度高；受惠於 eTNGA 底盤及 2,850mm 長軸距設計，前後排乘客距離有 1000mm；儀錶板及車廂內多處以高級纖維織布包裹讓駕乘者更感靜謐。同時，全景天幕連電動幕簾讓駕駛者的視野更開揚。標準配備前排冷暖通風座椅及雙區域自動恆溫冷氣系統。車內多處收納空間也盡得其用，加上 441 公升特大尾箱連腳控電尾門，兩層底板靈活實用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209506 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209509 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前後排乘客距離有 1000mm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209508 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲儀錶板及車廂內多處以高級纖維織布包裹讓駕乘者更感靜謐</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>電池容量達 71.4 kWh 續航力達 436 公里</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">全輪驅動的 bZ4X 是首部搭載 eTNGA 純電車型專屬底盤的車款，設計上將行車電池裝置在車底；底盤與電池一體化的設計，使 bZ4X 重心更低並且平均分配重量和位置，也提高車架剛性、操控性能及駕駛安全。廠方設計輕量化車身，亦讓力量傳遞更精準。bZ4X 採用由豐田與 Panasonic 共同研發及製造的行車電池，容量 71.4kWh，具備電池冷卻功能，續航力高達 436 公里。快速充電由 10%-80% 只需短短 30 分鐘，全新的電能驅動系統，最大馬力輸出 203（150kW）、最大扭力達  266Nm。而 bZ4X 配備剎車動能回收系統，讓駕駛者能夠自由選擇動能回收的時間。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209512 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲續航力高達 436 公里。快速充電由 10%-80% 只需短短 30 分鐘</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">bZ4X 的娛樂配備和行車科技包括：7 吋全電子儀錶及多功能顯示屏、12.3 吋原廠輕觸式屏幕音響系統連無線 Apple CarPlay 及原廠導航系統、原廠 JBL 高級音響系統連 9 個喇叭、Qi 電話無線充電裝置、前排放射式加熱系統、豐田首度採用的旋鈕式排檔等；其中 7 吋全電子儀錶及多功能顯示屏更是採用全新佈局，從用家角度出發，駕駛時觀看儀錶更方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209507 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209510 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲7 吋全電子儀錶及多功能顯示屏更是採用全新佈局，從用家角度出發，駕駛時觀看儀錶更方便</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209511 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲豐田首度採用的旋鈕式排檔</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>新增了司機監測系統，獨立鏡頭監測司機動態</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">bZ4X 配備第 3 代豐田主動式安全系統（Toyota Safety Sense™️3.0），首次新增了司機監測系統，以獨立鏡頭監測司機動態，在可能發生潛在危險時作主動提醒。另外，升級的行車雷達及鏡頭，大大提升監察能力，使預警式防護系統可於更遠的距離輔助駕駛者，甚至作自動剎車。bZ4X 也標準配置了 9 個安全氣袋、8 個前後泊車警示器、泊車防碰撞輔助系統、原廠 360 度全景泊車影像系統等安全設備。bZ4X 更是香港首部豐田型號引入自動泊車輔助系統 （Advanced Park），不論 L 位或 S 位都可輕鬆解決泊車疑難。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209513 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港首部豐田型號引入自動泊車輔助系統 （Advanced Park）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><u>ALL-NEW bZ4X 售價：</u><u><br /></u>HK$ 349,860 （一換一後售價）</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

